vote.title: Authorize an Interlocal Agreement with Dallas College, for the period of September 14, 2023 through December 31, 2024, with two (2) one-year renewal options, approved as to form by the City Attorney, to provide workforce training of electrical vehicle repair and/or electrical vehicle charging station technicians - Not to exceed $250,000.00 - Financing: General Fund
